01:31:13,552 --> 01:31:16,180
"Dear Lord, as I stumble
through this life,"

2427
01:31:16,305 --> 01:31:18,515
"help me to create more laughter
than tears,"

2428
01:31:18,640 --> 01:31:20,476
"dispense more happiness
than gloom,"

2429
01:31:20,601 --> 01:31:22,769
"spread more cheer
than despair."

2430
01:31:22,895 --> 01:31:25,314
"Never let me become so blase
that I will fail to see"

2431
01:31:25,439 --> 01:31:27,316
"the wonder
in the eyes of a child"

2432
01:31:27,441 --> 01:31:29,776
"or a twinkle
in the eyes of the aged."

2433
01:31:29,902 --> 01:31:32,404
"Never let me forget that my work
is to cheer people,"

2434
01:31:32,529 --> 01:31:35,199
"make them happy,
and make them laugh."

2435
01:31:35,491 --> 01:31:37,451
"Never let me acquire success
to the point"

2436
01:31:37,576 --> 01:31:39,786
"where I discontinue
calling on my Creator"

2437
01:31:39,912 --> 01:31:41,247
"in the hour of need,"

2438
01:31:41,413 --> 01:31:42,581
"and acknowledging Him
and thanking Him"

2439
01:31:42,706 --> 01:31:44,208
"in the hour of plenty."

2440
01:31:44,500 --> 01:31:47,419
"And in my final moment,
may I hear you whisper,"

2441
01:31:47,544 --> 01:31:50,380
" 'When you made my people smile,
you made me smile.' "

